question: Given: 2. public class Bunnies {  3. static int count = 0;  4. Bunnies() {  5. while(count < 10) new Bunnies(++count);  6. }  7. Bunnies(int x) { super(); }  8. public static void main(String[] args) {  9. new Bunnies(); 10. new Bunnies(count); 11. System.out.println(count++); 12. } 13. } What is the result?
options: 9~10~11~12~Compilation fails.~ An exception is thrown at runtime.
